description: Yeti Frozen Custard brings a modern twist to a classic frozen favorite! Frozen custard is a very rich, creamy frozen dessert made with cream, sugar, and eggs. Like ice cream, it comes in a variety of flavors like our Lemon Lavender or Classic Bourbon Vanilla! By fusing together modern day artistic flavors and old-fashioned frozen custard, unique flavor combinations were created that tingle your taste buds and make people happy.Book the Yeti today and start your adventure!
name: Yeti Frozen Custard
